# Squad Locker / Le Vestiaire - Support

## Need help?

If you are experiencing an issue with the Squad Locker app, you can contact us:

📧 squadlocker.contact@gmail.com

We will do our best to answer your request as soon as possible.

## Common issues

### I can't log in

Make sure you are using the correct email address and password.
If you forgot your password, use the password recovery option.

### I can't find my team

Make sure you are logged into the correct account.
Ask your team manager to invite you if needed.

### I have an issue with a match or lineup

Please contact us and describe the issue you encountered.
Providing screenshots and details can help us resolve the problem faster.

## About Squad Locker

Squad Locker / Le Vestiaire is an app designed to help amateur football teams manage their season.

Create teams, organize matches, build lineups, and track player statistics in one place.
